      "number": 1,
      "id": "I_kwDOKFiMhc5uj_O-",
      "title": "use the term \"claims\" instead of \"data\" to represent the \"stuff\" inside a credential",
      "url": "https://github.com/leifj/vdcarch/issues/1",
      "state": "OPEN",
      "author": "leifj",
      "authorAssociation": "OWNER",
      "assignees": [
        "brentzundel"
      ],
      "labels": [],
      "body": "",
      "createdAt": "2023-08-17T12:41:52Z",
      "updatedAt": "2025-09-12T15:12:42Z",
      "closedAt": null,
      "comments": [
        {
          "author": "timcappalli",
          "authorAssociation": "COLLABORATOR",
          "body": "NIST uses attribute bundles too",
          "createdAt": "2025-08-26T14:25:03Z",
          "updatedAt": "2025-08-26T14:25:03Z"
        },
        {
          "author": "brentzundel",
          "authorAssociation": "COLLABORATOR",
          "body": "talked on 9/9 we're good with claims",
          "createdAt": "2025-09-09T14:36:25Z",
          "updatedAt": "2025-09-09T14:36:25Z"
        },
        {
          "author": "leifj",
          "authorAssociation": "OWNER",
          "body": "should we check with NIST ? do they feel strongly about their attribute bundles?",
          "createdAt": "2025-09-09T18:46:43Z",
          "updatedAt": "2025-09-09T18:46:43Z"
        },
        {
          "author": "timcappalli",
          "authorAssociation": "COLLABORATOR",
          "body": "@billfshr @ryang03 any thoughts?",
          "createdAt": "2025-09-10T18:27:59Z",
          "updatedAt": "2025-09-10T18:27:59Z"
        },
        {
          "author": "Ryang03",
          "authorAssociation": "NONE",
          "body": "I don't have a strong preference here. We used attribute bundles as a way to avoid the term credential because of how we currently used it in the document set and it would have been extremely challenging to unwind its uses across all four volumes. If the argument is that the content of a VDC is a signed set of claims about a user I think that is reasonable and consistent with many other descriptions. We would of course be fine with attributes (the individual elements) or attribute bundles (the signed package, more aligned to \"VDC\") but are also happy to go with consensus. ",
          "createdAt": "2025-09-12T15:12:42Z",
          "updatedAt": "2025-09-12T15:12:42Z"
        }
      ]
    },
